<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg/220px-Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="327" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg/330px-Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg/440px-Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg 2x" data-file-width="538" data-file-height="800" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Mandela_voting_in_1994.jpg" class="internal" title="Agrandir"></a></div>Nelson Mandela votant le <time class="nowrap" datetime="1994-04-27" data-sort-value="1994-04-27">27 avril 1994</time>.</div></div></div>
